{"tid":622573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人仔貶值】消息指中國考慮貶值人民幣以應對與美國貿易爭端","createTime":"2018-04-09T08:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T00:29:56.000Z","uid":54733,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"0d30d49cafd1fbb8326f091f36484725db30c7f3","tid":622573,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社９日專訊》中美貿易摩擦升溫，在中國考慮的應對措施中，據稱包括人民幣貶值這一選項。　　外電引述知情人士透露，中國正考慮用人民幣貶值應對當前與美國的貿易爭端。一些高級官員正在評估匯率貶值對出口、相關公司行業和經濟的潛在影響，並對不同貶值幅度產生的影響進行分析，評估還包括如果中美達成協議，是否需要貶值人民幣以降低對國內經濟的衝擊。　　知情人士又指，人民幣是否貶值及貶值多少將由最高領導層決定，同時取決於中美貿易爭端問題的進展。中國考慮的貶值方式可能是循序漸進，而非一次性，以降低對金融市場的衝擊。"},{"pid":"122e58460eff5a7792fdab8c1fc542917f167732","tid":622573,"uid":40628,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"五毛愛國份子，快啲入人民幣"},{"pid":"9f94d98eb1208c493cd644a92d7f651794ef0c7f","tid":622573,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"一貶會唔會通脹得好勁"},{"pid":"dea9a4b152a5ed63d62f320cd5407b1619762944","tid":622573,"uid":81795,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"貶到1:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2e55b062082ea74b6f2d64f6337df64418b8a6","tid":622573,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e018bccd0989de4c68c4ab951e8e56c60bc52b3","tid":622573,"uid":54733,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"早排咁辛苦升返少少 又要跌過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b3f56e3c3d2dcecf0de479ea39c4a52bac64ba","tid":622573,"uid":13303,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:56:48.000Z","msg":"光復上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{